criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  identified within the last 3 months with pre-diabetes which is defined as a fasting
             plasma glucose level of 5.6-6.9 mmol/L or a two-hour level after a 75 grams glucose
             load of 7.8-11 mmol/L based on the World Health Organization 1998 criteria;

          -  accessible by mobile phone that could receive Chinese text messages.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  a history of diabetes mellitus;

          -  currently on medicines known to alter glucose tolerance;

          -  did not have a mobile phone;

          -  unable to read Chinese characters;

          -  refused to take part in current study.
